!**************************************************************************
!! # Moirfeolaíocht na nAinmfhocail Gaeilge (Morphology of Irish Nouns)
!**************************************************************************
!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
!! +Idf is no longer used with base form .. just +DefArt after article ...
!**************************************************************************  
!
!!		C O N T I N U A T I O N     C L A S S E S
!
!**************************************************************************  
!!!LEXICON GuessNoun
!!!^GUESSNOUN	Nf2-SINGULAR;
!!!^GUESSNOUN	Nm1-1;
!!!^GUESSNOUN	Nf3-3;







